{{Italic title}}
'''''77: The Year of Punk and New Wave''''' (Helter Skelter Publishing, 2006) is a book by Henrik Poulsen that catalogues every [[punk rock]] band to have made a recording in the United Kingdom during the punk era.<ref>https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/features/az-of-1977-pops-jubilee-year-526249.html</ref> The book has about 200 entries starting with Acme Sewage Company and ending with the Zeros.<ref>https://www.straight.com/article/77-a-suitably-chaotic-read</ref>

